Turk shares ease 0 . 42 pct on political uncertainty . Istanbul shares eased in weak and range - bound trade on Tuesday as worries over the fate of the Islamist - led government persisted , brokers said . The IMKB National - 100 closed six points , or 0 . 42 percent lower at 1 , 435 after moving between 1 , 429 and 1 , 462 . Non - stop losses totalled 6 . 3 percent since the market opened on Thursday after a 6 - 1 / 2 day holiday . Trade volume firmed to 11 . 35 trillion lira from Monday ' s 9 . 55 trillion . 
